&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>Fetching: mini_portile2-2.0.0.gem &lt;span style="color:#f92672">(&lt;/span>100%&lt;span style="color:#f92672">)&lt;/span>
